content:
Scoring and activity data can help you make campaign decisions and optimize your marketing efforts. Assess people on engagement and fit with customizable scoring rules to help you identify your ideal customer. Plus, track web activity on sites outside of Marketing Cloud Growth when you set up external activity tracking.

Where: These changes apply to Salesforce Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Marketing Cloud Growth edition.

Track Engagement on External Sites

Marketing Cloud Growth can now track external web activity data, including form submissions and page views. To get started, configure external tracking in Marketing Cloud Growth Setup, and then add the generated code snippet to your website.

Customize Engagement and Fit Scoring Rules

Decide which criteria indicate that someone is ready to move on to the next phase of your sales funnel. Customize and build on the default scoring rules to adjust engagement and fit scores based on criteria you specify.
title: Track and Use Data to Inform Your Strategy
